data.description: **This beautiful home in Sunrise community is move in ready and such a Gem!**So many great details! New HVAC System, only one year, new water heater, new paint, new siding and a roof that is only four years old! The beautiful living room has high ceilings a fireplace as well as arched doorways. A separate dining area by kitchen with a sit in breakfast bar all open to the living area, great for entertaining! The garage was partially converted for larger laundry room and pantry. All the bedrooms have walk-in-closets! The owner has taken beautiful care of this house and it is ready for a new family. This is a Great corner lot with a huge backyard ready for a playscape, a pool or just a wonderful patio waiting for a great BBQ to happen! Come see you new home!
